<p>We assign a default name to hardware nodes that includes the model name and an arbitrary string of characters, but you can <a href='/docs/v2/our-platform/tutorials/organizations/handling-resources#05-Rename-Nodes'>rename the nodes in your organization</a>. You can also <a href='/docs/v2/our-platform/tutorials/organizations/handling-resources#06-Stop-Nodes'>stop running nodes</a> and select specific nodes to use when you run backtests, launch research notebooks, or deploy algorithms to live trading.</p>
